{"name": "Tranquil Chateau in the Heart of the Rhone Valley", "location": "Auvergne-Rh\u00f4ne-Alpes", "guests": "120 guests", "sleeps": "Sleeps 40", "from": "Lyon , 60 min", "misc[5]": "\u20ac From 9,500", "timestamp": 1669374964.7123878, "description": "DESCRIPTION\nOur beautiful 19th century Ch\u00e2teau in the heart of the Rh\u00f4ne Valley is surrounded by woods, fields and vineyards. Built in the Directoire (neoclassical era) style. We welcome you to sample the tranquility of our vast and secluded park, facing the Vercors mountains.\nIn the shadow of the chestnut trees, the gardens will invite you to wander the park where stand hundred-year-old trees. From there, under some lime and oak trees you will come accross multiple walking paths\u2026\nIn a successful marriage of historic stone and modernity, this Ch\u00e2teau is the dream setting for your special day. Hire the entire Ch\u00e2teau, or just part, to offer your guests unforgettable memories in the elegant surroundings of an idyllic country house.\nThe Ch\u00e2teau opens its doors to you for a romantic and festive stay in the company of your loved ones. On an area of more than 13 hectares, in the shade of its century-old trees, discover the magic of this timeless place for wedding festivities rich in emotions and memories.\nFor your big day, this amazing venue will provide you with a 150 m\u00b2 reception room. In exposed stones and old framework, its large bay windows will offer you a magnificent view of the swimming pool. Fully equipped with round tables and white Napoleon chairs, you can invite up to 120 people for a seated meal and up to 200 guests for cocktails.\nOutside, overlooking the splendid French garden in which you can take magnificent photos, the terrace will allow you to make your cocktail or your vin d'honneur in a green, country-style setting. The Ch\u00e2teau also has a fallback room of 100 m\u00b2 for your aperitif in case of bad weather or to be fitted out for children.\nThe Ch\u00e2teau team will be happy to welcome you for the celebration of the most beautiful day of your life. These professionals will take care of both you and your guests to make this weekend unforgettable.\nExtend your festivities until the end of the night thanks to the accommodation available at this Tranquil Ch\u00e2teau. A luxurious bridal suite will immerse you in a bubble of softness and elegance. Three large apartments with refined decoration will allow you to accommodate a large part of your guests on site and a large dormitory where up to 15 people can sleep in an unusual and chic decor. In total 40 people to spend the night on site.\nFor more information please do get in touch and we would be more than happy to help.", "images": ["https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/sophieaymeric-mariage-656_3_192839-165493961687072.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/sophieaymeric-mariage-986_3_192839-165493963036568.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/0036_mariage_alexia___niels_-_solophotographie_fr702_maselection_web-1024x675.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/0002_mariage_alexia___niels_-_solophotographie_fr002_maselection_web.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/mariage_aurane_benjamin_-_solophotographie_320.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/shooting_chavagnac_avril_2022_-_solophotographie002_copie.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/_chateau_de_chavagnac_-_juin_2020_-_solophotographie_042.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/0008_mariage_alexia___niels_-_solophotographie_fr057_maselection_web.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/0010_concert_chateau_chavagnac_juillet_21_-_solophotographie_fr_-011_web.jpg", "https://www.frenchweddingvenues.com/userfiles/venue/477/large/_chateau_de_chavagnac_-